            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ELove%20for%20a%20neighbor%20is%20always%20measured%20(as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20story%20of%20the%20Good%20Samaritan)%20in%20practical%20ways.%20Love%20for%20God%2C%20however%2C%20is%20often%20measured%20in%20impractical%20ways.%20In%20Martha's%20opinion%2C%20Mary%20was%20wasting%20her%20time%20sitting%20at%20the%20Lord's%20feet%20while%20the%20details%20in%20the%20kitchen%20required%20her%20attention%20(Luke%2010%3A39-40).%20The%20woman%20who%20lavished%20her%20ointment%20on%20the%20head%20of%20Jesus%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20being%20impractical%20and%20of%20wasting%20money%20(Matthew%2026%3A7-9).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20show%20our%20love%20for%20people%20by%20service.%20We%20show%20our%20love%20for%20God%20by%20worship.%20One%20who%20worships%20does%20not%20count%20the%20pennies%20or%20the%20hours%20but%20sees%20only%20the%20immense%20value%20of%20the%20Person%20he%20is%20worshiping.%20To%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20which%20measures%20everything%20by%20its%20efficiency%2C%20these%20dollars%20and%20hours%20seem%20wasteful.%20But%20to%20those%20who%20love%20God%20from%20their%20hearts%2C%20the%20money%20and%20time%20expended%20are%20only%20a%20trifling%20pittance.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20loving%20people%2C%20we%20must%20be%20very%20practical%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20worshiping%20God%2C%20we%20must%20lay%20aside%20our%20desire%20to%20be%20busy.%20In%20our%20love%20for%20God%2C%20let%20us%20detach%20ourselves%20from%20an%20earthly%20mentality.%20Even%20if%20our%20practical%2C%20reasoning%20side%20says%2C%20%22You're%20being%20wasteful%2C%22%20let's%20lavish%20our%20time%20and%20money%20upon%20the%20Lord%20in%20true%20worship.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
