            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDeuteronomy%2026%3A1-27%3A26%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_1%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDeuteronomy%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EHarvest%20Offerings%20and%20Tithes%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhen%20you%20enter%20the%20land%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20is%20giving%20you%20as%20a%20special%20possession%20and%20you%20have%20conquered%20it%20and%20settled%20there%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_2%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3Eput%20some%20of%20the%20first%20produce%20from%20each%20crop%20you%20harvest%20into%20a%20basket%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20designated%20place%20of%20worship%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20place%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20chooses%20for%20his%20name%20to%20be%20honored.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_3%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EGo%20to%20the%20priest%20in%20charge%20at%20that%20time%20and%20say%20to%20him%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWith%20this%20gift%20I%20acknowledge%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20that%20I%20have%20entered%20the%20land%20he%20swore%20to%20our%20ancestors%20he%20would%20give%20us.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_4%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20priest%20will%20then%20take%20the%20basket%20from%20your%20hand%20and%20set%20it%20before%20the%20altar%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_5%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20must%20then%20say%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BMy%20ancestor%20Jacob%20was%20a%20wandering%20Aramean%20who%20went%20to%20live%20as%20a%20foreigner%20in%20Egypt.%20His%20family%20arrived%20few%20in%20number%2C%20but%20in%20Egypt%20they%20became%20a%20large%20and%20mighty%20nation.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_6%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20Egyptians%20oppressed%20and%20humiliated%20us%20by%20making%20us%20their%20slaves%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_7%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3Ewe%20cried%20out%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20our%20ancestors.%20He%20heard%20our%20cries%20and%20saw%20our%20hardship%2C%20toil%2C%20and%20oppression.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_8%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20brought%20us%20out%20of%20Egypt%20with%20a%20strong%20hand%20and%20powerful%20arm%2C%20with%20overwhelming%20terror%2C%20and%20with%20miraculous%20signs%20and%20wonders.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_9%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20brought%20us%20to%20this%20place%20and%20gave%20us%20this%20land%20flowing%20with%20milk%20and%20honey!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_10%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20now%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20I%20have%20brought%20you%20the%20first%20portion%20of%20the%20harvest%20you%20have%20given%20me%20from%20the%20ground.%26%23x2019%3B%20Then%20place%20the%20produce%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20and%20bow%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20worship%20before%20him.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_11%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EAfterward%20you%20may%20go%20and%20celebrate%20because%20of%20all%20the%20good%20things%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20has%20given%20to%20you%20and%20your%20household.%20Remember%20to%20include%20the%20Levites%20and%20the%20foreigners%20living%20among%20you%20in%20the%20celebration.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_12%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BEvery%20third%20year%20you%20must%20offer%20a%20special%20tithe%20of%20your%20crops.%20In%20this%20year%20of%20the%20special%20tithe%20you%20must%20give%20your%20tithes%20to%20the%20Levites%2C%20foreigners%2C%20orphans%2C%20and%20widows%2C%20so%20that%20they%20will%20have%20enough%20to%20eat%20in%20your%20towns.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_13%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20you%20must%20declare%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20have%20taken%20the%20sacred%20gift%20from%20my%20house%20and%20have%20given%20it%20to%20the%20Levites%2C%20foreigners%2C%20orphans%2C%20and%20widows%2C%20just%20as%20you%20commanded%20me.%20I%20have%20not%20violated%20or%20forgotten%20any%20of%20your%20commands.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_14%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20have%20not%20eaten%20any%20of%20it%20while%20in%20mourning%3B%20I%20have%20not%20handled%20it%20while%20I%20was%20ceremonially%20unclean%3B%20and%20I%20have%20not%20offered%20any%20of%20it%20to%20the%20dead.%20I%20have%20obeyed%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20my%20God%20and%20have%20done%20everything%20you%20commanded%20me.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_15%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20look%20down%20from%20your%20holy%20dwelling%20place%20in%20heaven%20and%20bless%20your%20people%20Israel%20and%20the%20land%20you%20swore%20to%20our%20ancestors%20to%20give%20us%26%23x2014%3Ba%20land%20flowing%20with%20milk%20and%20honey.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_16%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Call%20to%20Obey%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Commands%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BToday%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20has%20commanded%20you%20to%20obey%20all%20these%20decrees%20and%20regulations.%20So%20be%20careful%20to%20obey%20them%20wholeheartedly.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_26_17%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20have%20declared%20today%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20your%20God.%20And%20you%20have%20promised%20to%20walk%20in%20his%20ways%2C%20and%20to